<tr>
<td>
<p><i>Discriminatory</i><br />
<a href="/wiki/Racial_segregation" title="Racial segregation">Racial</a>/<a href="/wiki/Religious_segregation" title="Religious segregation">Religious</a>/<a href="/wiki/Sex_segregation" title="Sex segregation">Sex segregation</a><br />
